00:00:00.790 --> 00:00:01.839
So to take away from this,

00:00:01.839 --> 00:00:05.520
the bottom line, is that there are a variety of different architectural styles

00:00:05.520 --> 00:00:08.080
that can be used to solve the same design problem.

00:00:09.130 --> 00:00:13.100
And, in order to figure out which one to use you should be

00:00:13.100 --> 00:00:17.510
aware that each style has it's advantages and disadvantages, and

00:00:17.510 --> 00:00:20.980
depending on the particular requirements, changes you have to deal with,

00:00:20.980 --> 00:00:23.980
you can pick the one that's best suited for your particular situation.

